BaseStation Controller Program for Mongol
Written by Allen Baker
    for Illinois Tech Robotics

***** Overview *****

Press "Ctrl + Q" to exit the program.

***** File Descriptions *****

***** Keyboard Control Scheme (no mouse)  *****

TURNING:

Turn Left           A
Turn Right          D

MOVING:

Move Forward        W
Move Backward       S
Strafe Left         Left-Shift + A
Strafe Right        Left-Shift + D
* NOTE: Mongol cannot turn while moving

AIMING:

Turn Gun Up         O
Turn Gun Down       L
Turn Gun Left       K
Turn Gun Right      ;

MISCELLANEOUS:

Fire                Right-Shift (hold)
Turbo               /


***** XBOX Gamepad Control Scheme *****

TURNING:

Turn Left           Left Joystick Left
Turn Right          Left Joystick Right

MOVING:

Move Forward        Right Trigger (hold)
Move Backward       Left Trigger (hold)
Strafe Left         Left Bumper (hold)
Strafe Right        Right Bumper (hold)
* NOTE: Mongol cannot turn while moving

AIMING:

Turn Gun Up         Right Joystick Up
Turn Gun Down       Right Joystick Down
Turn Gun Left       Right Joystick Left
Turn Gun Right      Right Joystick Right

MISCELLANEOUS:

Fire                A Button
Turbo               X Button
